channel.title: Fox Spirit - Azure Onyxscore [Dance, DnB, Classic Trance]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/azureonyx/fox-spirit
I've actually had fun making this track, mainly because of the newly released soundpack which included a classic piano.
This is inspired by the classic early 2000's hit songs that took over the radio. It still has an enormous impact of my childhood, but I am aware that's not the same with others.
But anyways, enjoy the track, this took less time than I was expecting it to be.
